### Dependency Management

<div class="row">
<div class="span7">
Managed dependencies are used to specify versions of dependencies if those versions are not specified in the <em>dependencies</em> list.
</div>

<div class="span5">
---YAML---
dependencyManagement:
- 'org.apache.ant:ant:1.8.3'
- 'junit:junit:4.11'
---YAML---
</div>
</div>

